# Package Manager

Always use **pnpm** in this project, never npm or yarn.

```bash
# ✅ GOOD
pnpm install
pnpm add <package>
pnpm run storybook

# ❌ BAD
npm install
yarn add <package>
```

The lockfile is `pnpm-lock.yaml`. Do not generate or reference `package-lock.json` or `yarn.lock`.
